      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GRAMMY'S SUNSHINE (4) is racing well this campaign with wins in two of her last three. Winning rider stays aboard and she is down a kilo. Will sit just off speed and should prove tough to hold out again. REGAL SECRET (2) raced on speed throughout last time and lifted strongly to hold off the challenge to score. Low draw and will give a sight again. LUJAEGO (6) is a progressive type who got off the mark fresh then led and nabbed late last time. Has upside and will give a sight again. STARMAE (7) will find this easier than her last couple and is overdue for a win. Nicely drawn and gets her chance. BOSSY STAR (1) is fitter for two runs back and should be ready to show something.",
